body:
CC: @TaoBi22 @fabianschuiki 
This change fixes the following bug:
https://github.com/llvm/circt/issues/8831


Example:
On this input:


```systemverilog
// circt-verilog
module Foo(input logic [1023:0] x);
  logic [7:0][63:0] a, b;
  always_comb {a, b} = x;
endmodule
````

`circt-verilog` used to crash, now it produces


```bash
ak2518@autobot:/local/scratch/ak2518/circt$ circt-verilog ../RTL-to-FSM-extractor/bad.sv
module {
  hw.module @Foo(in %x : i1024) {
    hw.output
  }
}
```
